Sentencas: In this work, a quantitative correlation between the adhesion strength and the ohmic resistance at the interfaces between the electrolyte and the cathode was established.
Titulo: Correlation of ohmic resistance and interfacial adhesion strength between cathode and electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A cell consisting of LSM/YSZ/LSM was used to tune the interface adhesion strength by changing the sintering temperature.
Titulo: Correlation of ohmic resistance and interfacial adhesion strength between cathode and electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Electrochemical impedance spectroscopy was used to measure the interfacial resistance.
Titulo: Correlation of ohmic resistance and interfacial adhesion strength between cathode and electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The interfacial adhesion strength was obtained by using a mechanical tensile test.
Titulo: Correlation of ohmic resistance and interfacial adhesion strength between cathode and electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The result shows that the ohmic area specific resistance decreases gradually with the increase of the adhesion strength at the interfaces and reaches a plateau at a certain value.
Titulo: Correlation of ohmic resistance and interfacial adhesion strength between cathode and electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: It seems that the polarization resistance has the similar changing trends with that of the ohmic resistance.
